take our tree.

10:43.917 --> 10:45.213
What's your problem, dude?

10:45.248 --> 10:48.315
Hey. What's going on, honey?

10:48.350 --> 10:50.757
I was just standing on my phone,
and that guy, he just dragged

10:50.792 --> 10:51.989
