12:34.621 --> 12:37.391
You watch<i> Die Hard,</i>
what, every day?

12:37.426 --> 12:41.131
What do you think, Bruce...
whatever his name is, would do?

12:41.166 --> 12:43.529
'80s action heroes,
they solve problems

12:43.564 --> 12:46.136
with violence and one liners.

12:46.171 --> 12:47.907
